 Search←{
     ∆Ref←⍺
     (ic ss full lf mhw sai)←⍵
    ⍝ 1: ic   = ignore container
    ⍝ 2: ss   = Search string
    ⍝ 3: full = "full text search" flag
    ⍝ 4: lf   = lower case flag
    ⍝ 5: mhw  = match whole words only
    ⍝ 6: sai  = search as is
     full:∆Ref FullSearch ss lf mhw sai     ⍝ Perform a full text search
     ∆Ref TitleSearch ss lf mhw sai
 ⍝ Performs a "Search" in "direction" on the global search
 ⍝ string  which is "_Data.searchString"
 }
